      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly everything just feels so empty. like i look at the world and there's just nothing there. no point to any of it, no higher purpose, just a bunch of atoms colliding until they don't anymore. it's just exhausting trying to pretend there's some kind of meaning when there clearly isn't.",
